at%20risk%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20AI%20will%20not%20eliminate%20them%20fully%2C%20rather%20it%20will%20lead%20to%20workforce%20transformation.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%20a%20quarter%20of%20the%2093%20respondents%20predict%20a%20steeper%20decline%20of%20between%205%25%20and%2010%25%20of%20total%20headcount.%20The%20peer%20group%20covered%20by%20BI%20includes%20Citigroup%20Inc.%2C%20JPMorgan%20Chase%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%20and%20Goldman%20Sachs%20Group%20Inc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20findings%20point%20to%20far-reaching%20changes%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20feeding%20through%20to%20improved%20earnings.%20In%202027%2C%20banks%20could%20see%20pretax%20profits%2012%25%20to%2017%25%20higher%20than%20they%20would%20otherwise%20have%20been%20-%20adding%20as%20much%20as%20%24180%20billion%20to%20their%20combined%20bottom%20line%20-%20as%20AI%20powers%20an%20increase%20in%20productivity%2C%20according%20to%20BI.%20Eight%20in%20ten%20respondents%20expect%20generative%20AI%20to%20increase%20productivity%20and%20revenue%20generation%20by%20at%20least%205%25%20in%20the%20next%20three%20to%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBanks%2C%20which%20have%20spent%20years%20modernizing%20their%20IT%20systems%20to%20speed%20up%20processes%20and%20shave%20costs%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20financial%20crisis%2C%20have%20been%20flocking%20into%20the%20new%20generation%20of%20AI%20tools%20that%20could%20further%20improve%20productivity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiti%20said%20in%20a%20report%20in%20June%20that%20AI%20is%20likely%20to%20displace%20more%20jobs%20across%20the%20banking%20industry%20than%20in%20any%20other%20sector.%20About%2054%25%20of%20jobs%20across%20banking%20have%20a%20high%20potential%20to%20be%20automated%2C%20Citi%20said%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20many%20firms%20have%20stressed%20that%20the%20shift%20will%20result%20in%20roles%20being%20changed%20by%20technology%2C%20rather%20than%20replaced%20altogether.%20Teres