tle%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fhefm5jhg_pritish-nandy_625x300_08_January_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20tribute%20by%20a%20fanboy%20who%20would%20memorise%20and%20recite%20many%20poems%20of%20Pritish%20Nandy%20(%3Cem%3EDa%3C%2Fem%3E)%20since%20the%201970s.%20Dada%2C%20travel%20well%20on%20your%20%E2%80%98Lonesong%20Street'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20you've%20crossed%20the%20bustling%20mainstreets%20of%20everever%20land%3Cbr%3E%5CnYou%20reach%20a%20lonesome%20sandstrip%20called%20the%20nevernever%20strand%3Cbr%3E%5CnThen%20you%20take%20the%20turning%20left%3Cbr%3E%5CnAnd%20you%20take%20the%20turning%20right%3Cbr%3E%5CnAnd%20where%20the%20twilight%20breaks%20you%20turn%20your%20ragged%20sight...%3Cbr%3E%5CnRound%20the%20duskfall%20where%20it's%20blue%3Cbr%3E%5CnLonesong%20Street%20waits%20for%20you%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20He%20Attended%20My%20Father's%20Funeral%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20teenager%20in%20high%20school%20in%20Calcutta%2C%20I%20always%20carried%20a%20ruled%20exercise%20book%20(%3Cem%3Ekhata%3C%2Fem%3E)%20in%20my%20school%20bag.%20Poems%20had%20to%20be%20composed.%20This%20is%20what%20dreams%20were%20made%20of.%20The%20inspiration%20was%20never%20TS%20Eliott%2C%20or%20WH%20Auden%2C%20or%20Robert%20Frost.%20Our%20folk%20hero%2C%20Pritish%20Nandy%2C%20was%20in%20his%20twenties.%20He%20wrote%20poems%20about%20the%20city%20he%20lived%20in%20and%20loved.%20It%20is%20unbelievable%20that%20five%20decades%20ago%2C%20he%20released%20an%20audio%20album%20of%20his%20poems%20read%20by%20Mallika%20Sarabhai%20and%20himself%2C%20with%20music%20composed%20by%20Ananda%20Shankar.%20Today's%20iTunes%20and%20Spotify%20fans%20who%20can%20upload%20a%20song%20with%20just%20a%20few%20clicks%20will%20find%20it%20difficult%20to%20even%20understand%20or%20comprehend%20the%20level%20of%20commitment%20and%20passion%20that%20was%20required%20to%20produce%20an%20audio%20LP%20(vinyl)%2050%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPritish%20da%20was%20a%20smorgasbord%20of%20knowledge%2C%20erudite%2C%20incisive%2C%20and%20always%20entertaining.%20The%20funny%20thing%20was%2C%20he%20was%20too%20old%20to%20be%20my%20buddy%20and%20too%20young%20to%20be%20my%20father's%20buddy.%20Yet%2C%20Pritish%20da%20always%20had%20time%20for%20the%20O'Briens%20of%20Kolkata.%20I%20was%20overwhelmed%20when%20he%20landed%20up%2C%20unannounced%2C%20for%20my%20father's%20funeral%20in%202016.%20In%20the%20middle%20of%20summer%2C%20he%20attended%20the%20service%20in%20Church%20and%20was%20at%20the%20burial%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20just%20had%20to%20be%20here%20to%20say%20farewell%20to%20your%20father%2C%20Neil%E2%80%9D.%20And%20as%20the%20sun%20set%20on%20that%20balmy%20summer%20afternoon%20at%20the%20Lower%20Circular%20Road%20Cemetery%2C%20in%20central%20Kolkata%2C%20there%20stood%20Pritish%20da%20near%20three%20of%20my%20uncles%20who%20were%20English%20professors.%20We%20weren't%20surprised%20that%20the%20beat%20poet%20of%20our%20generation%20was%20still%20quoting%20lines%20of%20immortal%20verse.%20How%20perfectly%20appropriate.%20Thomas%20Grey's%20Elegy%20%3Cem%3EWritten%20in%20a%20Country%20Churchyard.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20curfew%20tolls%20the%20knell%20of%20parting%20day%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20lowing%20herd%20wind%20slowly%20o'er%20the%20lea%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20ploughman%20homeward%20plods%20his%20weary%20way%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnAnd%20leaves%20the%20world%20to%20darkness%20and%20to%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPoet%2C%20painter%2C%20publisher%2C%20producer%2C%20parliamentarian%2C%20Padma%20Shri%2C%20he%20was%20a%20maverick%20in%20the%20truest%20sense%20of%20the%20word.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20a%20long%20chat%20a%20few%20months%20ago%20during%20the%20pujo%20of%202024.%20I%20was%20trying%20to%20convince%20him%20to%20write%20his%20autobiography.%20There%20were%20so%20many%20stories%20that%20had%20to%20be%20told%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20plane%20ride%20from%20Mumbai%20where%20he%20was%20seated%20next%20to%20a%20media%20baron.%20The%20chance%20meeting%20changed%20his%20life%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20story%20behind%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray%20sending%20him%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20on%20a%20Shiv%20Sena%20ticket%20in%201998%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHis%20favourite%20anecdotes%20from%20his%20days%20as%20editor%20of%20The%20Illustrated%20Weekly%20of%20India.%20Also%2C%20Filmfare%2C%20The%20Independent%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20creation%20and%20growth%20of%20Pritish%20Nandy%20Communications%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHis%20love%20for%20stray%20dogs%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20wonderful%20women%20in%20his%20life%20(chuckle)%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20call%2C%20I%20remember%20asking%20him%20what%20he%20would%20most%20like%20to%20be%20remembered%20as%E2%80%94poet%2C%20publisher%2C%20editor%2C%20movie%20mogul%2C%20pet%20lover%2C%20or%20media%20personality.%20He%20was%20very%20clear%3A%20being%20a%20poet%20topped%20them%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet's%20leave%20you%20with%20a%20poem%20Pritish%20Nandy%20wrote%20about%20a%20city%20he%20deeply%20loved%2C%20despite%20all%20its%20imperfections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CCalcutta%20if%20you%20must%20exile%20me%20wound%20my%20lips%20before%20I%20go%3Cbr%3E%5CnOnly%20words%20remain%20and%20the%20gentle%20touch%20of%20your%20finger%20on%20my%20lips%20Calcutta%20burn%20my%20eyes%20before%20I%20go%20into%20the%20night%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20headless%20corpse%20in%20a%20Dhakuria%20bylane%20the%20battered%20youth%20his%20brains%20blown%20out%20and%20the%20silent%20vigil%20that%20takes%20you%20to%20Pataldanga%20Lane%20where%20they%20will%20gun%20you%20down%20without%20vengeance%20or%20hate%3Cbr%3E%5CnCalcutta%20if%20you%20must%20exile%20me%20burn%20my%20eyes%20before%20I%20go%3Cbr%3E%5CnThey%20will%20pull%20you%20down%20from%20the%20Ochterlony%20monument%20and%20torture%20each%20broken%20rib%20beneath%20your%20upthrust%20breasts%20they%20will%20tear%20the%20anguish%20from%20your%20sullen%20eyes%20and%20thrust%20the%20bayonet%20between%20your%20thighs%3Cbr%3E%5CnCalcutta%20they%20will%20tear%20you%20apart%20Jarasandha-like%3Cbr%3E%5CnThey%20will%20tie%20your%20hands%20on%20either%20side%20and%20hang%20you%20from%20a%20wordless%20cross%20and%20when%3Cbr%3E%5Cnyour%20silence%20protests%20they%20will%20execute%20all%20the%20words%20that%20you%20met%20and%20synchronised%3Cbr%3E%5CnCalcutta%20they%20will%20burn%20you%20at%20the%20stake%3Cbr%3E%5CnCalcutta%20flex%20the%20vengeance%20in%20your%20thighs%20and%20burn%20silently%20in%20the%20despair%20of%20flesh%3Cbr%3E%5CnIf%20you%20feel%20like%20suicide%20take%20a%20rickshaw%20to%20Sonagachhi%20and%20share%20the%20sullen%20pride%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20women%20who%20have%20wilfully%20died%3Cbr%3E%5CnWait%20for%20me%20outside%20the%20Ujjala%20theatre%20and%20I%20will%20bring%20you%20the%20blood%20of%20that%20armless%20leper%20who%20went%20mad%20before%20hunger%20and%20death%20met%20in%20his%20wounds%3Cbr%3E%5CnI%20will%20show%20you%20the%20fatigue%20of%20that%20woman%20who%20died%20near%20Chitpur%20out%20of%20sheer%20boredom%20and%20the%20cages%20of%20Burrabazar%20where%20passion%20hides%20in%20the%20wrinkles%20of%20virgins%20who%20have%20aged%20waiting%20for%20a%20sexless%20war%20that%20never%20came%3Cbr%3E%5CnOnly%20obscene%20lust%20remains%20in%20their%20eyes%20after%20time%20has%20wintered%20their%20exacting%20thighs%3Cbr%3E%5CnAnd%20I%20will%20show%20you%20the%20hawker%20who%20died%20with%20Calcutta%20in%20his%20eyes%3Cbr%3E%5CnCalcutta%20if%20you%20must%20exile%20me%20destroy%20my%20sanity%20before%20I%20go%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Derek%20O'Brien%2C%20MP%2C%20leads%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of