ed%20'good'%2C%2051%20and%20100%20'satisfactory'%2C%20101%20and%20200%20'moderate'%2C%20201%20and%20300%20'poor'%2C%20301%20and%20400%20'very%20poor'%2C%20and%20401%20and%20500%20'severe'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20IMD%2C%20Delhi's%20minimum%20temperature%20was%20recorded%20at%209.6%20degrees%20Celsius.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20weather%20agency%20said%20the%20capital's%20maximum%20and%20minimum%20temperatures%20would%20hover%20between%206%20and%2020%20degrees%20Celsius%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EGrap%20Stage%203%20In%20Delhi-NCR%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre's%20panel%20on%20Delhi-NCR's%20air%20quality%20on%20Thursday%20re-implemented%20stage%203%20curbs%20under%20the%20Graded%20Response%20Action%20Plan%20(GRAP)%20amid%20a%20sharp%20rise%20in%20air%20pollution%20levels%20owing%20to%20unfavourable%20meteorological%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi's%20air%20pollution%20levels%20showed%20an%20increasing%20trend%20with%20the%2024-hour%20average%20air%20quality%20index%20(AQI)%20clocking%20357%20at%204%20pm%20on%20Thursday%2C%20up%20from%20297%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Commission%20for%20Air%20Quality%20Management%2C%20responsible%20for%20strategising%20air%20pollution%20mitigation%20in%20Delhi-NCR%2C%20directed%20authorities%20in%20the%20region%20to%20immediately%20implement%20curbs%20prescribed%20under%20stage%203%20to%20prevent%20further%20worsening%20of%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-weather-pollution-curbs-under-grap-3-re-imposed-in-delhi-as-air-quality-declines-7437765%5C%22%3EGRAP%20Stage%203%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20revoked%20on%20Sunday%2C%20entails%20a%20ban%20on%20non-essential%20construction%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClasses%20up%20to%20grade%20V%20are%20required%20to%20shift%20to%20hybrid%20mode%20under%20Stage%203.%20Parents%20and%20students%20have%20the%20option%20to%20choose%20online%20education%20wherever%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20Stage%203%2C%20BS-III%20petrol%20and%20BS-IV%20diesel%20cars%20(4-wheelers)%20are%20restricted%20in%20Delhi%20and%20nearby%20NCR%20districts.%20Persons%20with%20disabilities%20are%20exempt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStage%203%20also%20bans%20non-essential%20diesel-operated%20medium%20goods%20vehicles%20with%20BS-IV%20or%20older%20standards%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20winters%2C%20the%20Delhi-NCR%20region%20enforces%20restrictions%20under%20GRAP%2C%20which%20categorises%20air%20quality%20into%20four%20stages%20-%20Stage%20I%20(Poor%2C%20AQI%20201-300)%2C%20Stage%20II%20(Very%20Poor%2C%20AQI%20301-400)%2C%20Stage%20III%20(Severe%2C%20AQI%20401-450)%2C%20and%20Stage%20IV%20(Severe%20Plus%2C%20AQI%20above%20450).%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736477220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fvvgt6ddg_delgi-fog_625x300_10_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdense-fog-envelops-delhi-ncr-again-aqi-drops-to-severe-category-7439769%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dense%20fog%20enveloped%20parts%20of%20the%20Delhi-National%20Capital%20Region%20(NCR)%20this%20morning%2C%20reducing%20visibility%20to%20zero%20and%20affecting%20flight%20and%20train%20operations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdense-fog-envelops-delhi-ncr-again-aqi-drops-to-severe-category-7439769%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dense%20fog%20blankets%20Delhi-NCR%2C%20flights%20delayed%20due%20to%20zero%20visibility%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736477084000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-ncr-weather-dense-fog-zero-visibility-igi-airport-flights-delayed-125011000120_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indira%20Gandhi%20International%20Airport%20in%20Delhi%2