the%20matches%20of%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20in%20Pakistan.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20Dubai%20International%20Cricket%20Stadium%20will%20be%20hosting%20India's%20matches%20in%20the%20tournament%20as%20the%20side%20has%20opted%20not%20to%20travel%20to%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20renovation%20works%20at%20the%20venues%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20which%20started%20in%20August%20last%20year%20and%20were%20supposed%20to%20be%20completed%20by%20December%2031%2C%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20concluded.%20Several%20reports%20have%20claimed%20if%20the%20venues%20are%20not%20ready%20for%20handover%20on%20February%2012%2C%20the%20entire%20tournament%20will%20be%20shifted%20to%20the%20UAE.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20ongoing%20concerns%20for%20Pakistan%2C%20a%20big%20relieving%20report%20for%20them%20has%20come%20to%20the%20fore.%20A%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fstory%2Fchampions-trophy-pakistan-stadium-rennovation-india-practice-game-dubai-2662192-2025-01-09%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fa%3E%20stated%20that%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20is%20closely%20monitoring%20the%20status%20of%20the%20three%20stadiums%20in%20Pakistan%20and%20that%20its%20delegation%20has%20not%20raised%20any%20concern%20regarding%20it%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20eight-team%20tournament%2C%20featuring%2015%20contests%2C%20will%20conclude%20on%20March%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20work%20(related%20to%20stadiums)%20will%20be%20done%20by%20the%20first%20week%20of%20February.%20Pakistan%20will%20successfully%20host%20the%20Champions%20Trophy.%20No%20need%20to%20go%20by%20any%20rumours.%20We%20are%20committed%20to%20giving%20our%20best.%20There%20are%20people%20who%20are%20trying%20to%20tarnish%20Pakistan's%20image%20on%20social%20media.%20We%20know%20who%20all%20they%20are%20and%20why%20they%20are%20doing%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20PCB%20official%20told%20IANS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20PCB%20on%20Wednesday%20moved%20the%20ODI%20tri-series%2C%20also%20involving%20South%20Africa%20and%20New%20Zealand%2C%20from%20Multan%20to%20Karachi%20and%20Lahore%2C%20saying%20the%20move%20was%20due%20to%20the%20advanced%20stage%20of%20preparations%20at%20Lahore's%20Gaddafi%20Stadium%20and%20Karachi's%20National%20Stadium%2C%20which%20will%20host%20six%20of%20the%2012%20Champions%20Trophy%20group%20stage%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20is%20preparing%20to%20host%20an%20ICC%20tournament%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%201996%2C%20when%20it%20co-hosted%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20IANS%20Inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736476680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F1bkahnh_champions-trophy-2024-prediction_625x300_08_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Fchampions-trophy-to-be-moved-out-of-pakistan-report-says-icc-delegation-7436242%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20have%20been%20several%20media%20reports%20stating%20that%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20might%20be%20shifted%20out%20of%20Pakistan%20due%20to%20delay%20in%20renovation%20work%20at%20the%20stadiums%20in%20the%20country.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A31%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Fchampions-trophy-to-be-moved-out-of-pakistan-report-says-icc-delegation-7436242%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Taylor's%20LA%20mansion%20safe%20amid%20Palisades%20wildfire%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736476362000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117102075%2Cimgsize-45678.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fpalisades-wildfire-is-taylor-swifts-lavish-la-mansion-safe-amid-the-catas