0whose%20house%20was%20one%20of%20just%20a%20handful%20left%20standing%20on%20a%20burned-out%20Altadena%20street%20told%20AFP%20said%20he%20was%20working%20with%20his%20neighbors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20so%20stressed%20about%20this%20looting%20happening%20all%20around%20that%20my%20neighbors%20were%20on%20watch%20all%20last%20night%20for%20several%20houses%20in%20the%20neighborhood%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20man%2C%20who%20did%20not%20want%20to%20give%20his%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20supposed%20to%20take%20over%20for%20them%20tonight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELos%20Angeles%20County%20Sheriff%20Robert%20Luna%20said%20his%20officers%20were%20pushing%20into%20fire-wrecked%20areas%20and%20evacuation%20zones%20to%20try%20to%20deter%20wrongdoers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20continue%20to%20conduct%20roving%20patrols%2C%20manning%20hard%20road%20closures%2C%20providing%20security%20in%20evacuation%20areas%20to%20prevent%20anyone%20who%20may%20be%20tempted%20to%20engage%20in%20criminal...%20behavior%20like%20looting%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20bar%20for%20arresting%20people%20in%20an%20evacuation%20zone%20was%20low%2C%20and%20warned%20that%20his%20officers%20would%20pounce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20have%20an%20evacuation%20order%20by%20law%2C%20if%20you%20remain%20in%20that%20area%2C%20you%20are%20guilty%20of%20a%20misdemeanor.%20If%20you%20commit%20certain%20crimes%2C%20it%20could%20jump%20up%20to%20a%20felony%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20are%20in%20one%20of%20these%20areas%20and%20you%20do%20not%20belong%20there%2C%20you%20are%20going%20to%20be%20subject%20to%20arrest.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELos%20Angeles%20County%20District%20Attorney%20Nathan%20Hochman%20said%20anyone%20the%20sheriff's%20department%20handed%20over%20to%20his%20office%20would%20be%20dealt%20with%20severely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C