ash%20Deep%2C%20Prasidh%20Krishna%2C%20Harshit%20Rana%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar%20Reddy%20took%2040%20scalps%20in%20351%20overs%2C%20with%20their%20average%20and%20strike-rate%20reading%2034.82%20and%2052.6%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20inexperience%20of%20pacers%20and%20over-reliance%20on%20Bumrah%20does%20raise%20questions%20on%20India's%20fast-bowling%20stocks%20for%20the%20future.%20Sunil%20Joshi%2C%20ex-India%20spinner%20and%20chief%20selector%20during%20India's%202-1%20series%20victory%20in%20Australia%20in%202020%2F21%2C%20is%20optimistic%20about%20the%20fast-bowling%20prospects%20but%20felt%20India%20missed%20having%20a%20left-arm%20pacer%20in%20their%20line-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%2C%20because%20we%20already%20have%20Troy%20Cooley%2C%20he's%20been%20in%20NCA%2C%20and%20is%20looking%20after%20the%20fast%20bowling%20pool.%20So%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20there%20should%20be%20any%20worry.%20But%20definitely%2C%20we%20did%20miss%20a%20left-arm%20seamer%20in%20that%20line-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20a%20left-arm%20seamer%20would%20have%20been%20there%2C%20then%20there%20would%20have%20been%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20change%20in%20angles%20because%20most%20of%20the%20Australian%2C%20English%20or%20New%20Zealand%20batters%2C%20they%20are%20not%20very%20comfortable%20for%20the%20left-arm%20seamer%20because%20you're%20taking%20the%20ball%20away%20with%20a%20different%20angle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20just%20needed%20variety%2C%20but%20fortunately%20or%20unfortunately%2C%20both%20the%20bowlers%20Yash%20Dayal%20and%20Khaleel%20Ahmed%20were%20there%2C%20but%20they%20couldn't%20play%2C%20and%20that's%20unfortunate%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Joshi%20in%20an%20exclusive%20conversation%20with%20IANS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoshi%20recalled%20the%20time%20during%20the%202020%2F21%20series%2C%20where%20India%20were%20fielding%20tons%20of%20injuries%20to%20players%2C%20and%20the%20ones%20who%20went%20as%20net%20bowlers%20on%20tour%20went%20on%20to%20play%2C%20perform%2C%20and%20win%20games.%20Apart%20from%20the%20performances%20on%20the%20recent%20tour%2C%20India%20left%20a%20lot%20to%20be%20desired%20in%20terms%20of%20tactics%20to%20bowl%20to%20Australian%20batters%2C%20field%20placements%2C%20and%20bowling%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20all%20about%20showing%20character%20by%20each%20individual%20player%20who's%20on%20the%20tour%20to%20do%20well.%20For%20that%2C%20did%20we%20prepare%20very%20well%3F%20I%20think%20yes.%20Did%20we%20take%20responsibility%3F%20Yes.%20So%2C%20now%20from%20this%20tour%2C%20from%20the%20first%20Test%20match%20to%20the%20second%20and%20third%20matches%2C%20did%20we%20learn%20something%20from%20the%20opposition%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20look%20at%20it%20that%20way%20because%20if%20we%20learned%20something%20from%20the%20opposition%2C%20then%20yes%2C%20we%20could%20have%20been%20better%20and%20more%20consistent.%20If%20you%20have%20not%20learned%2C%20you%20need%20to%20look%20to%20explore%20that%20and%20be%20disciplined%20to%20put%20that%20efforts%20into%20perspective%20and%20practice%2C%20then%20make%20a%20result%20out%20of%20it%2C%20and%20that's%20how%20I%20looked%20at%20this%20tour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTactically%2C%20when%20it%20doesn't%20go%20well%2C%20then%20we'll%20be%20questioned.%20If%20it%20goes%20well%2C%20we%20say%20that%20okay%2C%20it's%20a%20good%20tactic%20used.%20We%20just%20need%20to%20look%20at%20what%20the%20opposition%20team%20did%20-%20like%20what%20are%20those%20tactical%20moves%20they%20did%20consistently%20well%3F%20Like%2C%20one%20can%20look%20at%20their%20fast%20bowlers%20or%20even%20at%20Nathan%20Lyon%20-%20he%20didn't%20do%20anything%2C%20he%20just%20kept%20his%20patience%20and%20his%20consistency.%20Did%20we%20do%20that%3F%20No%2C%20except%20Bumrah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAgain%2C%20except%20in%20phases%2C%20we%20have%20done%20consistently%20-%20be%20it%20Nitish%2C%20Siraj%2C%20Prasidh%20or%20Harshit%20Rana.%20So%20finally%2C%20we%20need%20to%20look%20at%20ourselves%20did%20we%20give%20the%20best%20shot%20in%20terms%20of%20being%20disciplined%3F%20Did%20I%20play%20my%20role%20in%20the%20team%20very%20clearly%3F%20I'm%20not%20looking%20at%20it%20from%20an%20outsider%20point%20of%20view.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20look%20at%2C%20'okay%2C%20being%20in%20the%20dressing%20room%2C%20did%20I%20put%20my%20best%20effort%3F%20Did%20I%20put%20my%20top%20A%20game%20in%20being%20disciplined%20in%20these%20situations%20or%20sessions%3F%20Did%20I%20play%20my%20role%20very%20clearly%20or%20this%20and%20that%20should%20have%20been%20done%3F'.%20So%20those%20are%20the%20very%20small%20things%2C%20because%20if%20you%20break%20down%20all%20these%20things%2C%20you'll%20be%20able%20to%20understand%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20elaborated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20development%20which%20left%20Joshi%20surprised%20on%20the%20tour%20of%20Australia%20was%20abrupt%20international%20retirement%20of%20off-spinner%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%2C%20after%20the%20third%20Test%20at%20the%20Gabba%20ended%20in%20a%20draw%2C%20a%20game%20he%20didn't%20feature%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20also%20felt%20very%20surprised%20by%20that%20because%20I%20don't%20know%20what%20transpired%20or%20prospered%20during%20or%20between%20the%20second%20and%20third%20Test%20matches.%20But%20it's%20again%20Ashwin%2C%20who%20has%20been%20very%20upfront%20in%20his%20decisions.%20So%20I'm%20not%20saying%20that%20it%20was%20a%20bad%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20mean%2C%20we%20need%20to%20respect%20that%2C%20because%20he%20has%20been%20a%20modern%20legend%20of%20the%20game%20and%20there's%20no%20doubt%20about%20it.%20But%20again%2C%20what%20transpired%20for%20him%20to%20do%20that%3F%20So%20obviously%2C%20we'll%20have%20to%20know%20because%20it%20was%20unbelievable%2C%20and%20the%20board%2C%20selection%20committee%2C%20and%20team%20management%20should%20answer%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3