.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EA%20Manhattan%20jury%20found%20he%20altered%20Trump%20Organization%20invoices%20and%20other%20records%20throughout%20his%20first%20year%20in%20office%20in%20order%20to%20retroactively%20hide%20a%20%24130%2C000%20hush%20money%20payment%20that%20silenced%20porn%20actress%20Stormy%20Daniels%20eleven%20days%20before%20the%202016%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20legal%20scholar%20stated%2C%20unequivocally%2C%20that%20this%20is%20a%20case%20that%20should%20never%20have%20been%20brought%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20in%20a%20Truth%20Social%20post%20Thursday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20no%20case%20against%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BThis%20was%20nothing%20other%20than%20Weaponization%20of%20our%20Justice%20System%20against%20a%20Political%20Opponent.%20It's%20called%20Lawfare%2C%20and%20nothing%20like%20this%20has%20ever%20happened%20in%20the%20United%20States%20of%20America%2C%20and%20it%20should%20never%20be%20allowed%20to%20happen%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3ESpeaking%20minutes%20after%20the%20SCOTUS%20order%20from%20Mar-a-Lago%2C%20Trump%20promised%20to%20appeal%20his%20conviction%20and%20repeated%20that%20the%20prosecution%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Battack%20on%20a%20political%20opponent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20much%20more%20important%20than%20tomorrow%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20his%20planned%20appeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20had%20fought%20hard%20to%20avoid%20sentencing%2C%20despite%20facing%20little%20inconvenience%20or%20penalty%20beyond%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrumps-nj-liquor-licenses-at-risk-again-if-sentenced-friday-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epotential%20issues%20with%20his%20New%20Jersey%20liquor%20licenses.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20week%2C%20his%20lawyers%20had%20argued%20in%20four%20courthouses%20%E2%80%94%20in%20Manhattan%2C%20Albany%2C%20and%20Washington%2C%20DC%20%E2%80%94%20that%20any%20invocation%20of%20presidential%20immunity%20automatically%20entitles%20Trump%20to%20a%20stay%20pending%20appeal%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffighting-hush-money-case-trump-says-presidents-elect-are-immune-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeven%20before%20he%20is%20sworn%20in%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20opposition%20filings%2C%20Manhattan%20prosecutors%20scoffed%20at%20the%20idea%20that%20%26quot%3Bpresident-elect%20immunity%26quot%3B%20is%20even%20a%20thing.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupreme-court-trump-immunity-january-6-election-ruling-decision-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20US%20Supreme%20Court's%20landmark%20July%201%20opinion%3C%2Fa%3E%20granted%20presidents%20broad%20immunity%20from%20prosecution%2C%20but%20made%20no%20mention%20of%20immunity%20prior%20to%20swearing%20in%2C%20lawyers%20for%20Bragg%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDefendant's%20novel%20invocation%20of%20President-elect%20immunity%20does%20not%20warrant%20his%20Court's%20premature%20intervention%26quot%3B%20in%20an%20ongoing%20state%20criminal%20case%2C%20Bragg%20told%20the%20high%20court%20in%20papers%20filed%20Thursday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDefense%20lawyers%20have%20promised%20to%20file%20a%20post-sentencing%20appeal%20of%20the%20conviction%2C%20with%20SCOTUS%20if%20necessary%2C%20given%20what%20they%20say%20were%20violations%20of%20Trump's%20constitutional%20rights%20prior%20to%20and%20during%20the%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20primary%20example%2C%20they%20say%20grand%20jurors%20and%20trial%20jurors%20in%20the%20hush-money%20case%20improperly%20heard%20evidence%20that%20includes%20acts%20Trump%20took%20in%20his%20official%20role%20as%20president%2C%20which%20prosecutors%20are%20now%20barred%20from%20using.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20official-act%20evidence%2C%20all%20from%202018%2C%20includes%20tweets%20Trump%20sent%2C%20a%20federal%20form%20he%20signed%2C%20and%20a%20conversation%20he%20had%20in%20the%20Oval%20Office%20with%20Hope%20Hicks%2C%20his%20communications%20director.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20and%20the%20trial%20judge%2C%20Merchan%20have%20argued%20that%20even%20if%20this%20was%20official-act%20evidence%2C%20it%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bharmless%20error%26quot%3B%20to%20share%20it%20with%20jurors%2C%20given%20the%20other%20overwhelming%20proof%20of%20guilt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscotus-allows-trumps-ny-hush-money-sentencing-proceed-friday-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736468233000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67802dde50dfd88e193db379%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscotus-allows-trumps-ny-hush-money-sentencing-proceed-friday-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20Supreme%20Court%20rejected%20Trump's%20request%20to%20delay%20sentencing%20in%20his%20New%20York%20hush-money%20case.%20He'll%20face%20zero%20penalties%20and%20can%20attend%20virtually.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22litaliano%40insider.com%20(Laura%20Italiano)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A178%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscotus-allows-trumps-ny-hush-money-sentencing-proceed-friday-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Maps%20and%20pictures%20chart%20how%20fires%20have%20spread%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736468225000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Fdffc%2Flive%2Ff17f69e0-ce66-11ef-9fd6-0be88a764111.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcg525q2ggl4o%232%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Maps%20and%20images%20showing%20how%20the%20fires%20currently%20affecting%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20area%20are%20developing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1333%2C%