%3EThis%20was%20well%20before%20hunting%20was%20outlawed%20in%201972.%20The%20jungle%20formed%20a%20prized%20destination%20for%20hunting%20expeditions.%20And%20the%20family%20would%20often%20join%20in%3B%20Billy%20Arjan%20included.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20young%20boy%E2%80%99s%20targets%20were%20small%20animals%2C%20scurrying%20to%20escape%20his%20watchful%20eye.%20But%20as%20he%20grew%20older%2C%20his%20targets%20matured%20too.%20Soon%2C%20he%20was%20aiming%20at%20owlets%2C%20hyaenas%2C%20leopards%2C%20and%20tigers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20is%20more%20compelling%20than%20the%20%3Cem%3Eshikari%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20(hunter)%20exploits%20is%20the%20story%20of%20his%20redemption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBilly%20Arjan%20recalls%20his%20forties%20as%20the%20last%20time%20he%20picked%20up%20a%20rifle.%20As%20he%20shared%20in%20an%20interview%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20finally%20stopped%20shooting%20in%201960%20when%20I%20was%20overcome%20with%20remorse%20for%20ending%20the%20life%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F343873%2Fwildlife-photographer-naturalist-in-ladakh-karamjeet-singh-snow-leopards-himalayan-brown-bear-endangered-species%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20beautiful%20leopard%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20headlights%20of%20my%20jeep.%20I%20had%20no%20right%20whatsoever%20to%20destroy%20what%20I%20could%20not%20create.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETapping%20on%20this%20sentiment%2C%20he%20gravitated%20to%20the%20other%20end%20of%20the%20spectrum%20%E2%80%94%20conservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057