ner%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F267251%2Fvaccinate-sex-workers-transgenders-domestic-help-free-covidactioncollab-coronavirus%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egetting%20medical%20help%3C%2Fa%3E.%20On%20one%20such%20visit%20to%20a%20hospital%2C%20Noori%20saw%20a%20poster%20on%20HIV%20and%20AIDS%2C%20urging%20people%20to%20get%20tested%2C%20and%20stating%20that%20there%20is%20no%20cure%20for%20the%20disease.%20%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20handle%2010%20to%2015%20clients%20daily%20and%20I%20wondered%20why%20this%20was%20such%20a%20deadly%20disease%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9COn%20July%2022%2C%201987%2C%20I%20was%20the%20second%20person%20to%20be%20tested%20positive%20for%20HIV%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FTBI-featured-image-8_11zon-1736169095.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Noori%20spending%20some%20quality%20time%20with%20the%20kids%20at%20the%20shelter%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FTBI-featured-image-8_11zon-1736169095.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FTBI-featured-image-8_11zon-1736169095-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FTBI-featured-image-8_11zon-1736169095-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FTBI-featured-image-8_11zon-1736169095-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FTBI-featured-image-8_11zon-1736169095-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-395669%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENoori%20has%20invested%20in%20a%20space%20worth%20Rs%203%20crore%20for%20the%20children.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctors%20told%20Noori%20that%20she%20would%20live%20only%20for%20a%20year%20or%20two.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20disheartened%20for%20a%20week%2C%20but%20Dr%20Usha%20Raghavan%20came%20to%20my%20tiny%20house%20searching%20for%20me%2C%20provided%20counselling%20and%20educated%20me%20about%20the%20condition%2C%20which%20changed%20my%20perspective%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20adopted%20three%20kids%20from%20a%20commercial%20sex%20worker%2C%20so%20I%20decided%20to%20live%20for%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Raghavan%2C%20who%20saw%20Noori%20struggling%20to%20make%20ends%20meet%20financially%2C%20secured%20her%20a%20job%20at%20the%20STD%20department%20in%20Chennai%E2%80%99s%20Government%20Hospital.%20%E2%80%9CI%20learnt%20to%20retrieve%20blood%2C%20dress%20wounds%2C%20and%20identify%20medicines%2C%E2%80%9D%20Noori%20says.%20%E2%80%9CDr%20Raghavan%20provided%20a%20monthly%20amount%20of%20Rs%20800%2C%20which%20was%20essential%20for%20my%20survival.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Raghavan%20also%20encouraged%20her%20to%20join%20the%20Community%20Action%20Network%20as%20an%20outreach%20worker.%20Despite%20her%20tireless%20efforts%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20HIV%2C%20Noori%20faced%20severe%20isolation%20and%20discrimination.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20given%20pig%E2%80%99s%20fodder%20to%20eat%20as%20lunch%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls%20a%20disheartening%20experience%20during%20an%20outreach%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELiving%20with%20HIV%20often%20brings%20its%20own%20set%20of%20hurdles.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20stigma%20surrounding%20both%20my%20transgender%20identity%20and%20HIV%20status%20led%20many%20to%20fear%20and%20ostracise%20me%20and%20my%20friends%2C%20Selvi%2C%20Indira%2C%20and%20Pazhani%2C%20who%20were%20also%20living%20with%20the%20virus.%20I%20hated%20it%20when%20doctors%2C%20who%20are%20well%20aware%20of%20the%20nature%20of%20disease%2C%20ill-treat%20their%20patients%2C%E2%80%9D%20Noori%20says.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20treated%20us%20like%20dogs%2C%20throwing%20stones%20at%20us%2C%20thinking%20that%20it%20is%20transmitted%20like%20the%20flu%20virus.%20I%20wanted%20to%20change%20that%20perspective%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Noori%20continued%20undeterred%2C%20raising%20awareness%20about%20HIV%20and%20advocating%20for%20the%20compassionate%20treatment%20of%20all%20individuals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-5-1734611396.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Noori%20holds%20over%2022%20leadership%20positions%20and%20possesses%20strong%20oratory%20and%20logical%20skills.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-5-1734611396.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-5-1734611396-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-5-1734611396-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-5-1734611396-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-5-1734611396-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-390996%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENoori%20holds%20over%2022%20leadership%20positions%20and%20possesses%20strong%20oratory%20and%20logical%20skills.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20outreach%20worker%2C%20Noori%20started%20conducting%20meetings%20for%20people%20affected%20by%20HIV.%20It%20was%20during%20one%20of%20these%20meetings%20that%20she%20met%20Dr%20Joseph%20Williams%2C%20the%20then-director%20of%20VHS%20Hospital.%20Together%2C%20they%20established%20the%20South%20India%20Positive%20Network%2C%20an%20NGO%20for%20which%20Noori%20was%20elected%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDr%20Williams%20was%20instrumental%20in%20this%20endeavour%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Noori.%20%E2%80%9CNot%20only%20did%20he%20guide%20us%20through%20the%20registration%20process%20but%20also%20provided%20crucial%20support%20in%20setting%20up%20the%20organisation.%20I%20consider%20him%20a%20trusted%20mentor%20even%20today.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202001%2C%20for%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20State%20AIDS%20Control%20Society%2C%20Noori%20submitted%20a%20proposal%20to%20aid%20HIV%20positive%20individuals%2C%20written%20under%20the%20guidance%20of%20Dr%20Williams.%20She%20was%20able%20to%20secure%20the%20project%20to%20provide%20support%20and%20care%2C%20worth%20Rs%203.12%20lakh%20for%20their%20upliftment%2C%20and%20she%20executed%20the%20same%20skillfully%20with%20just%20three%20staff%20members.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20worked%20on%20over%2010%20projects%20and%20I%20was%20promoted%20to%20a%20position%20where%20I%20could%20recruit%20more%20than%2070%20staff.%20I%20have%20good%20oratory%20skills%20which%20have%20created%20an%20impact%20among%20the%20listeners%2C%20despite%20my%20poor%20educational%20background.%20This%20helped%20in%20my%20journey%20of%20leadership%2C%E2%80%9D%20Noori%20beams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20shelter%20for%20the%20abandoned%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202003%2C%20Noori%2C%20supported%20by%20Dr%20Williams%2C%20established%20the%20SIP%20Memorial%20Trust.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20told%20me%20that%20I%20have%20good%20logical%20reasoning%20skills%2C%20so%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20be%20hesitant%20thinking%20about%20her%20lack%20of%20education%20to%20lead%20a%20trust%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Noori.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20other%20medical%20officials%20perceived%20my%20identity%20as%20just%20a%20transwoman%20who%20is%20HIV%20positive%2C%20Dr%20Joseph%20saw%20my%20potential%20and%20motivated%20me%20to%20start%20the%20trust%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%20I%20named%20the%20trust%20SIP%20in%20memory%20of%20my%20three%20friends%20%E2%80%94%20Selvi%2C%20Indira%2C%20and%20Pazhani%20%E2%80%94%20who%20tragically%20lost%20their%20lives%20to%20HIV%2C%E2%80%9D%20Noori%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20the%20Trust%20aimed%20to%20create%20awareness%20and%20outreach%20for%20HIV%20positive%20individuals.%20Later%2C%20Noori%20started%20focusing%20on%20rescuing%20infants%20and%20children%20who%20were%20abandoned%20because%20of%20HIV.%20%E2%80%9CHaving%20experienced%20a%20challenging%20childhood%20myself%2C%20I%20deeply%20understand%20the%20lasting%20impact%20that%20parents%20and%20caregivers%20have%20on%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20mindset.%20These%20children%20are%20not%20to%20blame%20for%20their%20HIV%20status%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FThumbnail_v1kdhj_1563274483_11zon-1734611645.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Noori%20has%20dedicated%20her%20life%20for%20these%20children%2C%20saving%20nothing%20for%20herself.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FThumbnail_v1kdhj_1563274483_11zon-1734611645.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FThumbnail_v1kdhj_1563274483_11zon-1734611645-300x226.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FThumbnail_v1kdhj_1563274483_11zon-1734611645-500x376.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FThumbnail_v1kdhj_1563274483_11zon-1734611645-768x577.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FThumbnail_v1kdhj_1563274483_11zon-1734611645-800x600.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FThumbnail_v1kdhj_1563274483_11zon-1734611645-600x450.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FThumbnail_v1kdhj_1563274483_11zon-1734611645-400x300.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FThumbnail_v1kdhj_1563274483_11zon-1734611645-200x150.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FThumbnail_v1kdhj_1563274483_11zon-1734611645-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-391006%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22812%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENoori%20has%20dedicated%20her%20life%20for%20these%20children%2C%20saving%E2%80%9DI%20haven%E2%80%99t%20saved%20anything%20for%20myself.%20All%20I%20do%20right%20now%20is%20for%20them%20and%20their%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares%20with%20a%20smile.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20always%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20mother.%20Providing%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F338067%2Fbengaluru-transwoman-helps-abandoned-eldery-orphans-food-shelter-ngo-nammane-summane-impact-appeal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebetter%20livelihood%20and%20nurturing%3C%2Fa%3E%20them%20gives%20me%20the%20satisfaction%20of%20making%20crucial%20changes%20in%20society%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20baby%20I%20rescued%20was%20a%20two-day-old%20female%20child%20near%20the%20Governmental%20Hospital.%20The%20parents%20had%20left%20a%20note%20saying%20this%20child%20is%20HIV%20positive%20and%20is%20a%20disgrace%20to%20the%20family.%20I%20decided%20to%20provide%20a%20good%20living%20for%20the%20child%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20recalling%20the%20incident%20that%20happened%20in%202006.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20goal%20was%20to%20help%20children%20with%20HIV%20understand%20that%20it%20was%20just%20another%20health%20condition%2C%E2%80%9D%20Noori%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CI%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20the%20disease%20to%20define%20them.%20I%20wanted%20them%20to%20be%20treated%20with%20the%20same%20care%20and%20respect%20as%20any%20other%20child.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trust%20provides%20a%20comfortable%20home%20for%20children%20who%20have%20tested%20positive%20for%20HIV.%20%E2%80%9CSome%20are%20brought%20in%20by%20their%20parents%2C%20some%20are%20abandoned%2C%20and%20some%20are%20sent%20from%20hospitals%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%E2%80%9D%20Noori%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20been%20able%20to%20save%20over%20400%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F277718%2Fnakshatra-changemaker-inspiring-transwoman-bengaluru-destitute-orphans-ngo%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echildren%20affected%20by%20HIV%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20helped%20them%20with%20education%2C%20medicines%2C%20food%2C%20shelter%2C%20and%2C%20most%20importantly%2C%20love%20and%20affection.%20Noori%20has%20invested%20in%20a%20space%20worth%20Rs%203%20crore%20for%20the%20children.%20%E2%80%9CI%20haven%E2%80%99t%20saved%20anything%20for%20myself.%20All%20I%20do%20right%20now%20is%20for%20them%20and%20their%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares%20with%20a%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNoori%20%3Cem%3Eaaya%3C%2Fem%3E%20(grandma)%20has%20always%20prioritised%20education%20and%20encouraged%20me%20to%20study%20three%20degrees%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Naga%20Thejas%2C%20who%20grew%20up%20at%20SIP%20Memorial%2C%20and%20is%20currently%20pursuing%20his%20master%E2%80%99s%20in%20social%20work%2C%20hoping%20to%20start%20his%20own%20NGO%20to%20support%20people%20in%20need.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20600px)%20100vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https